> vt run script1 # cache miss
$ vtt print-file foo.txt
initial content
> vt run script2 # cache hit, same command as script1
$ vtt print-file foo.txt ◉ cache hit, replaying
initial content

---
vt run: cache hit.
> vtt replace-file-content foo.txt initial modified # modify shared input

> vt run script2 # cache miss, input changed
$ vtt print-file foo.txt ○ cache miss: 'foo.txt' modified, executing
modified content
> vt run script1 # cache hit, script2 already warmed cache
$ vtt print-file foo.txt ◉ cache hit, replaying
modified content

---
vt run: cache hit.
